dc_title_s: Zoning Fond du Lac County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data group represents zoning for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2020 and includes the layers 'FOND_DU_LAC_AIRPORT_2020', 'FOND_DU_LAC_GENERAL_2020', and 'FOND_DU_LAC_SHORELAND_2020'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://www.fdlco.wi.gov/departments/departments-f-m/land-information/data-download
